# LeagueofDowningAPI
LeagueofDowningAPI is a service for retrieving information on characters, items, or players

# Group Champions
Notes related resources of the **LeagueofDowningAPI**

## Champions Collection [/api/champions/?offset={offset}&limit={limit}]

+ Parameters
    + offset (required, number, `1`) ... number `offset` of the champion to perform action with. Has example value.
    + limit (required, number, `1`) ... number `limit` of the champion to perform action with. Has example value.



### List first {limit} champions starting from {offset}. Queries are bounded by the number of champions which is 3 [GET]
